  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (adversarial W-AR-02)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all nominally meeting required levels per decision rationale), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). One factor carries a structured level shortfall masked by extended qualitative justification.",
